==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Respecter
<hw>Re*spect"er</hw> <pr>(-?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
respects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>A respecter of persons</b></col>, <cd>one who regards or
judges with partiality.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Of a truth I perceive that God is no <qex>respecter of
persons</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Acts x. 34.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Respectful</ent>⟦br⟧
